snippet.title: Hero for the New Season, Cateye Erika!
snippet.description:
Pre-register for New Season: https://tap.io/qMYTdRnD

She specialized in rapid movement in combat, dodging attacks, and giving enemies the lethal blow.  
Be sure to check her out in the New Season！

The story of the new season takes place in the endless Sea of Void, and the biggest challenge we will face this season will be the Lord of the Void Sea, the king of pirates, who leads the fleet to plunder the realm, and the countless crew members that he enslaves.

Offer the "Void Sea Night Flame", unlock a certain number of "Void Sea Seal". Hunters can go to the Void Sea End Port to challenge the "Bride of Void Sea", and snatch the treasure she's been hoarding.

If you are lucky enough to get the ticket “Void Sea Invitation” from the "Bride of Void Sea", you will be able to challenge the final boss of the season, Lord of Void Sea, who will drop several unique Legendary items.

Hunters, bring your brave determination and see you in the new season on January 12th!

Official Website: https://torchlight.xd.com/en/ep2
#torchlightinfinite 
#blacksail
